    "value": "Birthplace",
}
</code></pre><h2 id='delete-a-person-attribute-sub-resource'>Delete a person attribute sub resource</h2>
<ul>
<li>Delete or void a target attribute. Returns <code>404 Not Found</code> status if the person does not exist. 
If not authenticated or authenticated user does not have sufficient privileges, a <code>401 Unauthorized</code> 
status is returned.</li>
</ul>
<pre class="highlight shell_session"><code>DELETE /person/:target_person_uuid/person/:target_attribute_uuid
</code></pre>